Beispiel Projekt fuer die SDCgit@github.com:ghiottolino/SDC_Planner.git


STEPS:

1) Create new Android Project, fill in all fields
SDC Planner
com.seitenbau.demo (com.seitenbau.android.sdc.planner)?
SessionListActivity (TalkListActivity)

2) Create new packages: 
com.seitenbau.demo.data
com.seitenbau.demo.beans
com.seitenbau.demo.adapter

3) Generated the Session Bean
*private String title;	
*private String room;
*private String speakers;
*private Calendar fromTime;
*private Calendar toTime;
*private String teaser;

4) Copy the content of the data package from a copy of the project to the new created project
The package contains the file sessions.xml, xml parsing class, a TestData static class with return the list of all Sessions.

(Improve the layout formatting, add default text to the textfield)

4) Copy views (main + talklist_item view) for list activity

5) Create TalkListAdapter extends ArrayAdapter<Session>
* Create constructor, pass the list
* Override getView method

6) Add method getSubtitle to Session bean

7) Customize TalkActivity

* set layout
* fetch listview
* fetch sessions
* add adapter to listview

8) Show in emulator


9) Copy layout "talk_details.xml". Possibly make some changes using the editor

10) Create a new TalkDetailActivity
* set the layout
* retrieves all text views
* make Session = bull
* write session fields in views

11) Add onItemClickListener to ListActivity

12) Add Intent and startActivity to onClick method

13) Add Activity to Manifest









7) Added talk details view

8) Defined new activity in the manifest

9) Added intent between list and talk view.
